03:37.150 --> 03:39.950
Really?

03:39.950 --> 03:42.840
Instead,

03:42.840 --> 03:46.090
- I will have to stop writing for a while.
 <i>- Ah, seriously!</i>

03:46.090 --> 03:50.760
No, you can't! Who stops writing with only one final episode left to complete?!

03:50.760 --> 03:52.340
