<i>- You are acting. Your acting skill has improved lately.</i> 
 - Assistat Manager Yoon! Assistant Manager Yoon, 911!

04:04.110 --> 04:09.110
Ah, Assistant Manager Yoon!
 <i> Thirty, an age everyone will face one day.</i>

04:09.110 --> 04:13.590
Assistant Manager Yoon! 
 <i>Still clumsy and strange,</i>

04:13.590 --> 04:17.420
<i>we are thirty. 
 Episode 1: How to be Thirty</i>

04:20.740 --> 04:25.640
- Congrats on meeting your deadline.
- It's not something to congratulate.

04:25.640 --> 04:27.890
You want to say that you will have a new manager, right?

04:27.890 --> 04:29.770
It was my last request.

04:29.770 --> 04:34.180
But you saw the reaction, right? Everyone is going nuts about how refreshingly satisfying it is.

04:34.180 --> 04:36.330
Writer!

04:37.340 --> 04:40.170
Ah, I heard that you had a hard time because of the demonstration.

04:40.170 --> 04:42.110
Sorry.

04:42.110 --> 04:46.090
Even just thinking about it...

04:46.090 --> 04:50.560
I'm saying this because I care for you, Writer.

04:50.560 --> 04:55.380
