<i>Ah, really?! I really did enter...</i>

05:16.550 --> 05:18.740
<i>I think the file is not being uploaded.</i>

05:18.740 --> 05:21.830
<i>The deadline was five minutes ago.</i>

05:21.830 --> 05:25.510
