05:25.510 --> 05:28.210
<i>It's Seo Ji Won.</i>

05:28.210 --> 05:31.290
<i>It's entry number 3006. Ah, really?!</i>

05:31.290 --> 05:36.080
<i>Yes, it's that one. Thank you. Thank you so much!</i>

05:39.630 --> 05:41.350
Writer?

05:44.780 --> 05:47.650
Did you remember the old days?

05:47.650 --> 05:49.900
No, I was just...

05:49.900 --> 05:53.940
