06:26.050 --> 06:27.130
<i>Like a Watercolor</i>

06:34.120 --> 06:39.170
Oh! Look at these dialogues. What should I do now?

06:39.170 --> 06:42.760
I wrote these? No way!

06:42.760 --> 06:45.500
I didn't, right?

06:45.500 --> 06:51.130
