06:54.100 --> 06:55.920
"Don't like me."

06:55.920 --> 07:00.710
Ugh!!

07:00.710 --> 07:02.410
"What is that?"

07:02.410 --> 07:05.230
"Don't like me."

07:05.230 --> 07:07.370
"How exactly do you do that?"

07:07.370 --> 07:11.570
Oh my, what do I do? Ew!

07:11.570 --> 07:13.270
Writer.

07:19.020 --> 07:20.530
- You're here. 
 - Yes.

07:20.530 --> 07:23.640
Why are you alone?

07:26.010 --> 07:31.630
What a shame! You made an effort coming here to meet the new manager, but he can't be here because something came up.

07:31.630 --> 07:34.440
Oh is that it?

07:34.440 --> 07:36.660
It can't be helped.

07:36.660 --> 07:39.280
Writer! Do you know that?

07:39.280 --> 07:43.430
The new manager is totally sold on your new proposal.

07:43.430 --> 07:47.970
Our CEO put in real effort to recruit him.

07:47.970 --> 07:50.430
This proposal...

07:50.430 --> 07:52.420
Assistant Manager Yoon, I thought about it carefully.

07:52.420 --> 07:56.110
How about we do something else other than this? I can't—

07:56.110 --> 07:57.720
Sorry.

08:01.620 --> 08:04.110
Hello.

08:04.110 --> 08:07.860
I really don't have the confidence to do the next project.

08:07.860 --> 08:10.400
Ah, Assistant Manager Lee Seung Yu.

08:10.400 --> 08:12.970
<i>Yes. Assistant Manager Yoon, did you eat?</i>

08:12.970 --> 08:16.910
<i>I'm sorry. I'm supposed to be there, but I couldn't go.</i>

08:18.570 --> 08:21.490
Assistant Manager Lee Seung Yu?

08:25.500 --> 08:29.290
It couldn't possibly be that Lee Seung Yu, right?

08:30.810 --> 08:32.610
No.

08:32.610 --> 08:34.610
It's not possible.

08:34.610 --> 08:37.800
There are so many people with the same name in this world.

08:44.650 --> 08:46.350
Seo Ji Won.

08:46.350 --> 08:48.050
Let's go together.

08:57.740 --> 09:00.240
<i>Da capo</i>

09:21.720 --> 09:23.270
Are you okay?

09:46.070 --> 09:51.580
You heard the name Lee Seung Yu once and let your imagination run wild?

09:51.580 --> 09:54.810
If it's to that extent, then it's your fantasy, my friend.

09:54.810 --> 09:56.930
Hey! What do you mean by fantasy?

09:56.930 --> 10:02.170
I mean, does it even make sense that you'd meet your first love again as your manager?

10:02.170 --> 10:04.960
Those kinds of coincidences only happen in dramas.

10:04.960 --> 10:07.510
But do you guys know that

10:07.510 --> 10:10.960
dramas don't lie?

10:10.960 --> 10:16.080
Oh my, then were you expecting to be able to work and have a romance too? Like buy one get one free deal?

10:16.080 --> 10:20.120
- Oh, our Writer Seo is ambitious.
 - I was just imagining, that's all.

10:20.120 --> 10:24.010
Saying "I like you" to each other in high school...

10:24.010 --> 10:25.650
is something like that considered love?

10:25.650 --> 10:30.410
Everyone, there is no love in this world even when you share yourself emotionally and physically with someone.

10:30.410 --> 10:33.290
That's why... it's a romance comic.

10:33.290 --> 10:35.910
- Exactly. 
 - We're thirty now.

10:35.910 --> 10:38.600
Don't you think that we need at least "29"?
 (T/N: Korean adult books/videos are rated "19")

10:38.600 --> 10:43.040
I don't understand how she actually became an announcer. Her words are way too harsh.

10:43.040 --> 10:47.640
