10:49.800 --> 10:53.500
Hey! You're the really pitiful one.

10:53.500 --> 10:57.170
The guy you dated for two years cheated on you with a girl he went out with for just three months.

10:57.170 --> 11:03.200
Yes, he really was a bastard, to whom Hong Ah Yeong gave up her twenties.

11:03.200 --> 11:08.500
