11:20.490 --> 11:23.450
<i>You're like a puppy.</i>

11:23.450 --> 11:25.790
He was a real bastard!

11:25.790 --> 11:29.500
And... trash.

11:29.500 --> 11:30.670
Me?

11:30.670 --> 11:35.650
