11:35.650 --> 11:38.600
No, not the men,

11:38.600 --> 11:40.810
- I'm talking about you. 
 - Hey!

11:40.810 --> 11:44.800
<i>Please go out with me.</i>

11:44.800 --> 11:48.790
<i>So annoying.</i> 
 I agree.

11:48.790 --> 11:52.460
- I agree. 
 - As for me, I'm sick of men now.

11:52.460 --> 11:55.140
Then why are you dreaming of meeting your first love again?

11:55.140 --> 11:57.240
I just imagined it, okay?

11:57.240 --> 12:02.520
Ah, I don't need anything! I will make this cafe a success and season two of my life!

12:02.520 --> 12:03.710
I will make a colorful leap!

12:03.710 --> 12:07.750
Oh, our President Hong, you are something else.

12:07.750 --> 12:12.930
Then, in season two of my life, I should just experience an awesome love with an awesome guy.

12:12.930 --> 12:16.570
Then, what could be our Writer Seo's goal?

12:16.570 --> 12:20.070
Goal? Well...

12:21.350 --> 12:27.750
Well, you know me. I'm a well-known writer who works on one webtoon after another.

12:27.750 --> 12:31.020
Would there be a need for a goal?

12:31.020 --> 12:34.680
- You'll have to stop me, or I'll really end up killing her today.
 - Don't come near.

12:34.680 --> 12:37.800
You'll just have to hit rock bottom to come to your senses.

12:37.800 --> 12:42.110
If that's case then,

12:42.110 --> 12:46.280
I do have a definite goal.

12:48.050 --> 12:50.810
So, are you in?

12:53.480 --> 12:56.640
Perfect for drinking with singing and dancing.

13:04.490 --> 13:08.010
♫ That's how life is.

